/* Resource script: bind the UTF-8 activeCodePage manifest into
 * webtransportd.exe. Resource ID 1 + type 24 (RT_MANIFEST) is the
 * magic pair Windows looks up when it loads an .exe, so with this
 * embedded the CRT's main() argv, getenv, and CreateProcessA all
 * interpret bytes as UTF-8 on Windows 10 1903+ (see memory
 * project_windows_utf8.md). The .rc file is compiled by windres
 * into a COFF .o under mingw; see the Makefile's Windows branch. */
1 24 "webtransportd.exe.manifest"
